23
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,319
I just received some news.

24
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,560
Director,

25
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:47,719
how did Chief Hirata die?

26
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,960
She was on her way

27
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,360
to the army hospital

28
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,120
when she was shot and killed.

29
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,520
There were three people in total.

30
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,680
Besides her,

31
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,439
