32
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,560
All of them were killed.

33
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,560
Didn't you go to the scene?

34
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,199
Yes.

35
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,080
That adjutant

36
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,520
was killed at close range with a knife-like weapon.

37
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,039
As for Hirata and the driver,

38
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:08,080
they were at close range

39
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,479
and were shot dead with a pistol.

40
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,759
I'm wondering

41
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,360
how these anti-Japanese elements

42
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:15,759
managed to get so close to her.

43
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,240
It was an inside job.

44
