50
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,759
Ten years ago

51
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:45,479
At a banquet for a high-ranking official in Shanghai

52
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:46,479
I met her

53
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,960
She came from an ordinary background

54
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,000
But her

55
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,280
ability to read people

56
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:52,319
truly impressed me

57
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:54,680
I recommended her to General Doihara

58
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:56,479
and sent her to Dong Jing

59
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,280
