67
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:20,839
Mr. Lu,

68
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,160
I'd like to hear your opinion.

69
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:25,160
I've already sent people to the military police.

70
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,720
