76
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:36,399
How could they still have so much power?

77
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:38,439
It might not be the Military Statistics Bureau.

78
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,639
These days,

79
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:42,079
the Communists are also very active.

80
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,360
These two assassinations

81
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,959
happened almost at the same time.

82
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:46,439
I've also sent people to Yagi Ryo's case.

83
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,839
Hopefully, they can find

84
