104
00:05:32,079 --> 00:05:33,079
Mr. Lu,

105
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,199
what's your view?

106
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,439
Based on my guess,

107
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,920
the person who assassinated Miss Hirata

108
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:42,720
is very likely the one we're looking for.

109
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:45,879
In the Japanese military police,

110
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,360
