there are indeed a few.

112
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:50,839
But to pull off something this ruthless,

113
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,399
it's hard to say.

114
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:58,839
Investigating the people around Hirata Kiko

115
00:05:58,839 --> 00:06:00,439
is the right approach.

116
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:03,000
But we must not limit ourselves to just the military police.

117
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:05,199
Hirata Kiko died very suddenly.

118
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,360
What does this indicate?

119
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:09,720
