123
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:20,199
I think you should look into

124
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:22,079
who Hirata Kiko was investigating

125
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:24,439
before she died.

126
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,120
Yes.

127
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,040
Yes.

128
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,240
I'll look into it right away.

129
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,319
You're awake.

130
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,199
Here.

131
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,360
