143
00:07:28,399 --> 00:07:30,120
Sister Man, you're such a good shot,

144
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,079
and you're beautiful,

145
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,399
smart and capable.

146
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:34,839
With you handling things,

147
00:07:34,839 --> 00:07:36,240
what could possibly go wrong?

148
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,079
You really know how to compliment people.

149
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,879
Here, take your medicine first.

150
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,879
Sister Man,

151
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,680
I'm just telling the truth.

152
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,920
You...

153
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,360
Don't you want to ask anything else?

154
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,560
You were the ones who saved me.

155
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,720
I'm really grateful.

156
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,680
I know you have your rules.

157
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:23,279
If I ask too much, it wouldn't be fair to you.

158
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,399
