161
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:31,360
I don't know where my future path leads.

162
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,240
But I just hope

163
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,399
I can truly help Liang Shuo.

164
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,000
Nian Ci

165
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:03,440
No matter which path you take,

166
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:06,000
as long as you follow your heart,

167
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,159
Liang Shuo said the same thing.

168
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,639
At this time,

169
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:16,120
