173
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,279
Take me back.

174
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,240
Where do you want to go?

175
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:36,720
Before he died, Hirata already suspected my relationship with Liang Shuo.

176
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:40,039
If I don’t show up there for a long time,

177
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,559
I’m afraid it will cause trouble for Liang Shuo.

178
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,399
Something so serious has happened.

179
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,840
The Japanese military police are already in that area

180
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,399
and have started a thorough search.

181
00:09:50,559 --> 00:09:52,039
I advise you not to go back yet.

182
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,080
No.

183
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,519
I have to go back.

184
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,399
Even though Hirata is dead,

185
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:58,000
Cui Mo still knows me.

186
00:09:58,159 --> 00:10:00,080
If I don’t show up for a long time,

187
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,480
they’ll eventually investigate there.

188
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:03,480
It will cause trouble for Liang Shuo.

189
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,200
Please take me back.

190
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:14,600
If that’s the case,

191
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,960
