00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,000
Okay.

196
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,480
Thank you.

197
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,159
Liang Shuo

198
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,320
Why are you in such a hurry?

199
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,519
There are so many things to deal with.

200
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,240
Just thinking about it gives me a headache.

201
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,679
And now this thing with Hirata Noriko happened.

202
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,320
I'm a newly appointed director.

203
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,480
I haven't even found my footing yet.

204
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,919
And now I've got a mess to clean up.

205
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:42,799
How could I not be anxious?

206
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:43,960
Busy as I am,

207
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,639
