216
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:02,440
Besides,

217
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,559
when it comes to you, Brother Cui,

218
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,919
if I had any clues,

219
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:06,600
