228
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,080
Yes, Director Hirata did suspect me.

229
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,519
But wasn't the misunderstanding cleared up quickly?

230
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,679
Besides,

231
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:31,240
after she came to the Special Operations Headquarters,

232
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:32,679
