233
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,159
Including you, Brother Cui.

234
00:11:35,559 --> 00:11:36,679
The personnel files

235
00:11:36,679 --> 00:11:38,039
were all thoroughly searched by her, weren't they?

236
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,200
If you ask me,

237
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:42,320
we still need to start from the scene of the incident.

238
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:43,799
Divide the area into sections

239
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:44,759
and investigate them one by one.

240
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,799
For now,

241
00:11:46,799 --> 00:11:48,000
that's all we can do.

242
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,080
How are your injuries?

243
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,320
Just flesh wounds.

244
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,039
It's nothing serious.

245
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,559
But speaking of which,

246
00:11:57,279 --> 00:11:59,399
I really didn't have the strength to kill anyone yesterday.

247
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,799
That sounded pretty sarcastic.

248
00:12:04,919 --> 00:12:06,279
You shouldn't have come today.

249
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:07,759
It would have been better to rest at home.

250
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:09,279
Alright.

251
00:12:09,279 --> 00:12:09,919
