565
00:28:28,359 --> 00:28:29,880
A new challenge.

566
00:28:30,240 --> 00:28:34,000
A new opportunity.

567
00:28:35,359 --> 00:28:40,359
I feel like I'm back at the military academy.

568
00:28:40,359 --> 00:28:42,559
Getting ready to face a big test.

569
00:28:43,119 --> 00:28:46,519
So the top priority right now

570
00:28:46,519 --> 00:28:52,519
is to root out these hateful traitors.

571
00:28:52,519 --> 00:28:53,720
In the future,

572
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:55,079
in my work,

573
00:28:55,599 --> 00:28:56,880
I will fulfill my duties,

574
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:59,000
work diligently,

575
00:28:59,279 --> 00:29:00,799
and stay grounded.

576
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:04,119
I will give my all to ensure I do not fail my mission.

577
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:14,880
We've found Miss Xie's residence.

578
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:16,440
Tonghai is already watching the place.

579
00:29:18,039 --> 00:29:19,200
Take a few more men with you.

580
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:20,400
Keep a close watch on her.

581
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,480
I'll be there soon.

582
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,480
Alright, understood.

583
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:51,960
Everything is finally tidied up.

584
00:29:52,359 --> 00:29:53,680
Everything has been restored to its place.

585
00:29:56,599 --> 00:29:57,880
Thank you so much, Sister Man.

586
00:29:59,519 --> 00:30:01,079
I've asked around the neighborhood.

587
00:30:01,319 --> 00:30:02,799
The reason you used to live here

588
00:30:02,799 --> 00:30:03,359
was also because

589
00:30:03,359 --> 00:30:05,000
everyone here works the night shift, right?

590
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:11,839
Luckily, none of them were here when it happened.

591
00:30:12,359 --> 00:30:13,480
So we're still relatively safe.

592
00:30:19,759 --> 00:30:21,799
If Number 76 gets suspicious of you,

593
00:30:21,799 --> 00:30:23,799
just say your stomach hurts so much you can't get out of bed.

594
00:30:27,839 --> 00:30:29,559
Here are the prescription and medicine from the hospital.

595
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,839
I'll put them in the drawer for you.

596
00:30:32,279 --> 00:30:32,880
Sister Man,

597
00:30:33,279 --> 00:30:34,519
you're really thoughtful.

598
00:30:37,880 --> 00:30:38,920
It's for safety.

599
00:30:39,319 --> 00:30:40,119
It's what I should do.

600
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,640
What you need to do now is get some good rest.

601
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:43,759
Listen to me.

602
00:30:43,759 --> 00:30:44,359
Go to sleep.

603
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:45,480
Okay.

604
00:30:46,079 --> 00:30:46,799
I'm leaving now.

605
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:31,799
Who is it?

606
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:33,480
Who’s there?

607
00:31:38,319 --> 00:31:38,920
Sister Man.

608
00:31:39,279 --> 00:31:40,319
Why are you back again?

609
00:31:40,319 --> 00:31:41,440
You’re being watched.

610
00:31:41,599 --> 00:31:42,720
I can’t leave either.

611
00:31:43,839 --> 00:31:44,720
What should we do then?

612
00:31:46,079 --> 00:31:47,559
Let’s hope they’re only watching.

613
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:49,559
I’ll wait until tonight to find a chance to leave.

614
00:31:58,759 --> 00:31:59,640
It’s Liang Shuo.

615
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:01,440
This is the knock pattern we agreed on.

616
00:32:13,599 --> 00:32:14,720
Why are you here?

617
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:15,759
There are spies downstairs.

618
00:32:15,759 --> 00:32:16,799
They all work for Cui Mo.

619
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,279
Cui Mo has seen me before.

620
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,240
I shouldn’t be here.

621
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,119
You can only stay here for now.

622
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,480
You can’t go anywhere.

623
00:32:28,119 --> 00:32:29,160
Better to die with honor

624
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,440
than to live in disgrace.

625
00:32:31,119 --> 00:32:32,440
At least I can’t drag you all down with me.

626
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,799
Everything is arranged.

627
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:50,799
It’s all set.

628
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,319
Director.

629
00:32:51,599 --> 00:32:52,440
What’s the plan?

630
00:32:52,839 --> 00:32:53,799
Hold your position.

631
00:32:54,359 --> 00:32:55,839
Come upstairs with me to take a look.

632
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:56,720
Yes.

633
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,319
We’re all brothers here.

634
00:32:59,559 --> 00:33:00,920
Let’s hope this doesn’t get ugly.

635
00:33:05,839 --> 00:33:06,440
Director.

636
00:33:07,559 --> 00:33:08,559
Here.

637
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,240
Director.

638
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,519
That room.

639
00:33:39,359 --> 00:33:40,319
Hide in the closet.

640
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:41,880
But they...

641
00:33:42,119 --> 00:33:42,839
We can only take a gamble.

642
00:33:42,839 --> 00:33:44,720
Bet that he hasn’t found any real evidence against me.

643
00:33:45,319 --> 00:33:45,759
Come.

644
00:33:46,599 --> 00:33:47,400
Stand to the left.

645
00:34:07,319 --> 00:34:08,159
Brother Liang,

646
00:34:08,719 --> 00:34:09,920
why are you back?

647
00:34:10,159 --> 00:34:10,960
Brother Cui,

648
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,559
what brings you here?

649
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:13,280
I thought

650
00:34:13,280 --> 00:34:15,320
I was the only one who slipped out of the venue.

651
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,079
As for me,

652
00:34:16,239 --> 00:34:17,079
I heard from others

653
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:18,599
that your wife wasn't feeling well.

654
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:19,920
So I hurried over to check on her.

655
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:21,440
You’re really quick.

656
00:34:21,559 --> 00:34:23,440
Brother Cui, your news travels even faster.

657
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:24,559
Indeed,

658
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:26,119
Yuxin is feeling a bit unwell.

659
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:27,480
So I sneaked back

660
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,519
to look after her.

661
00:34:29,079 --> 00:34:30,119
Sorry to trouble you.

662
00:34:30,119 --> 00:34:31,239
No need to be so polite.

663
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:32,320
Delun,

664
00:34:33,079 --> 00:34:34,639
check if Miss Xie’s things

665
00:34:34,639 --> 00:34:36,639
were all left in the car.

666
00:34:37,119 --> 00:34:37,719
Yes,

667
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:38,880
I’ll go get them right away.

668
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:40,880
Brother

669
00:34:41,599 --> 00:34:42,679
Let me see your wife.

670
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:43,440
Of course.

671
00:34:43,679 --> 00:34:44,400
Please come in.

672
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:45,880
Is that Brother Cui?

673
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:47,039
It's me.

674
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:48,920
Brother Cui.

675
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:49,719
I'm really sorry.

676
00:34:49,719 --> 00:34:50,840
I'm not feeling well.

677
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:51,239
Sister-in-law.

678
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:52,039
Sorry for the intrusion.

679
00:34:52,519 --> 00:34:53,480
What's wrong with you?

680
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:54,480
A sudden illness.

681
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,519
My gastritis flared up again.

682
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,760
That's a problem with eating habits.

683
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:59,039
Your wife is from Wuxi.

684
00:34:59,039 --> 00:35:00,559
She doesn't eat spicy food like people from Chongqing, right?

685
00:35:00,760 --> 00:35:01,880
She likes spicy food, doesn't she?

686
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,639
Brother Cui.

687
00:35:05,639 --> 00:35:07,679
Why does that sound a bit odd?

688
00:35:08,719 --> 00:35:10,079
It sounds like there's a hidden meaning.

689
00:35:10,079 --> 00:35:11,000
Look at you.

690
00:35:11,079 --> 00:35:12,679
I'm just concerned about your wife.

691
00:35:14,079 --> 00:35:15,199
Don't be so sensitive.

692
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:25,719
Chicken soup.

693
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:27,199
Chicken soup is good.

694
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,119
It's nourishing.

695
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:29,639
Brother.

696
00:35:30,119 --> 00:35:31,719
You're really good to your wife.

697
00:35:35,760 --> 00:35:37,000
It's just this room...

698
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:40,679
It's a bit unfair to your wife.

699
00:35:41,039 --> 00:35:42,280
It's too old.

700
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:43,760
This furniture...

701
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:44,519
Shouldn't it be replaced too?

702
00:35:44,519 --> 00:35:45,199
Brother Cui.

703
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:55,119
You suspect I'm hiding someone in this cabinet, don't you?

704
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:01,960
You should've said so earlier.

705
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:04,719
If you want to open it,

706
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,360
just do it directly.

707
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,800
Liang Shuo, it's all my clothes in there.

708
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:15,119
What are you doing?

709
00:36:15,119 --> 00:36:16,280
I'm not here to investigate.

710
00:36:16,519 --> 00:36:18,400
We're good brothers, right?

711
00:36:18,599 --> 00:36:19,519
You suspect me?

712
00:36:19,519 --> 00:36:21,039
No need to beat around the bush.

713
00:36:21,119 --> 00:36:22,000
Let me tell you,

714
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:24,320
Today, you have to get to the bottom of this for me.

715
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:26,000
Investigate thoroughly.

716
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:26,599
No, no, no.

717
00:36:26,599 --> 00:36:28,039
These are Yuxin's personal clothes.

718
00:36:28,039 --> 00:36:28,360
Come on.

719
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:28,639
Bro,

720
00:36:28,639 --> 00:36:30,119
Everyone knows these are my personal clothes.

721
00:36:30,119 --> 00:36:31,239
And you still want to open them?

722
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,119
He already said he's not here to investigate.

723
00:36:33,119 --> 00:36:33,800
Aren't you embarrassed?

724
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,880
I'm the one who's embarrassed.

725
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:36,039
We're family.

726
00:36:36,039 --> 00:36:36,760
He's not embarrassed.

727
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:37,719
Why should I be embarrassed?

728
00:36:37,719 --> 00:36:38,039
No, no, no.

729
00:36:38,039 --> 00:36:38,440
Come on, come on.

730
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,039
Brother, you—

731
00:36:39,039 --> 00:36:39,840
You have to look.

732
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:41,679
Look at you—

733
00:36:42,239 --> 00:36:43,679
You really make me feel ashamed.

734
00:36:43,719 --> 00:36:45,679
Brother, why go this far?

735
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:47,320
Let me tell you, Cui Mo,

736
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:49,159
Today you have to get to the bottom of this for me.

737
00:36:49,159 --> 00:36:50,679
Otherwise, just shoot me.

738
00:36:50,679 --> 00:36:52,039
So you won't keep overthinking all the time.

739
00:36:52,039 --> 00:36:52,760
Always being suspicious.

740
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:53,000
Come on.

741
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:53,880
Alright, alright, brother.

742
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:54,559
Brother.

743
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:55,119
No, no, no.

744
00:36:55,119 --> 00:36:55,480
Look.

745
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,199
You have to look.

746
00:36:56,199 --> 00:36:56,800
That's enough, brother.

747
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:57,360
This little bit doesn't matter.

748
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:57,679
Alright.

749
00:36:57,679 --> 00:36:58,320
Alright, brother.

750
00:36:58,320 --> 00:36:59,039
That's enough.

751
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:00,480
Sister-in-law.

752
00:37:00,880 --> 00:37:01,800
You've been wronged.

753
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:05,239
I was wrong.

754
00:37:06,079 --> 00:37:07,199
I was wrong, okay?

755
00:37:13,639 --> 00:37:14,679
We brothers—

756
00:37:14,679 --> 00:37:16,039
We've had so many years of friendship.

757
00:37:17,559 --> 00:37:18,960
If I don't trust anyone,

758
00:37:19,119 --> 00:37:20,360
how could I not trust you?

759
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:22,599
Me,

760
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:25,280
I really came here today just to see sister-in-law.

761
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,000
So I misunderstood Brother Cui.

762
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,880
That's right.

763
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:34,559
Come in.

764
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:43,679
Boss

765
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,360
I could only get these gifts.

766
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:47,079
There was really nothing else to buy downstairs.

767
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:50,000
They really are checking up on me.

768
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:54,840
Brother

769
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:56,840
Sorry about this.

770
00:37:57,280 --> 00:37:57,960
Sister-in-law

771
00:37:58,920 --> 00:37:59,639
Sorry for the offense.

772
00:38:02,559 --> 00:38:03,639
I'll wait for you downstairs.

773
00:38:21,719 --> 00:38:22,519
Come out.

774
00:38:28,199 --> 00:38:29,039
That was close.

775
00:38:29,679 --> 00:38:30,960
Will they come up again?

776
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:31,960
They probably won't.

777
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,880
But don't leave now.

778
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:35,119
Wait until it gets dark.

779
00:38:52,159 --> 00:38:52,880
Chief Cui

780
00:38:53,159 --> 00:38:54,840
Should the guys withdraw?

781
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:56,079
Leave a lookout.

782
00:38:56,079 --> 00:38:57,199
Keep an eye on this place for me.

783
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:59,920
I want to make sure no one else gets close.

784
00:39:00,199 --> 00:39:00,840
Yes.

785
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,800
Buy some braised snacks and other treats.

786
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:05,679
Send them up to Miss Xie.

787
00:39:07,159 --> 00:39:07,960
Chief Cui

788
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,039
With her illness,

789
00:39:09,039 --> 00:39:10,360
can she eat these things?

790
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,239
If she's really sick,

791
00:39:13,960 --> 00:39:15,159
of course she wouldn't eat them.

792
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,159
I understand.

793
00:39:17,159 --> 00:39:18,159
I'll take care of it right away.

794
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,119
Brother

795
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:23,960
How are things?

796
00:39:24,239 --> 00:39:25,360
Have you settled your wife?

797
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:27,320
If you don't give me an explanation,

798
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,559
I can't let this go.

799
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,280
As your older brother,

800
00:39:30,599 --> 00:39:31,719
I apologize to you.

801
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:35,360
The Japanese have been pressing us too hard.

802
00:39:35,400 --> 00:39:37,039
I've been so busy these days, I'm completely overwhelmed.

803
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,519
People below have been spreading rumors.

804
00:39:39,719 --> 00:39:41,400
That's why I suspected your wife.

805
00:39:41,599 --> 00:39:42,920
Spreading rumors?

806
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:46,400
We've been through life and death together for so many years.

807
00:39:47,039 --> 00:39:48,519
And you still don't trust me?

808
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,519
You'd sell me out over a few rumors?

809
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:52,760
I trust you one hundred percent.

810
00:39:53,239 --> 00:39:54,400
But the people around you,

811
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,239
I have to be cautious about them.

812
00:39:59,559 --> 00:40:00,679
From what I'm hearing,

813
00:40:01,079 --> 00:40:02,679
you're not suspecting me,

814
00:40:02,679 --> 00:40:04,119
but rather, you're worried about me.

815
00:40:04,440 --> 00:40:05,480
What do you think?

816
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:08,079
I really am worried about you.

817
00:40:09,719 --> 00:40:10,679
I think

818
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,519
your concern

819
00:40:13,079 --> 00:40:15,000
is making it a bit hard for me to breathe.

820
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:15,880
Brother, brother, brother,

821
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:16,679
alright, alright, alright.

822
00:40:17,599 --> 00:40:18,559
Just this once.

823
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,039
There won't be a next time.

824
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:20,880
Okay?

825
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:24,599
Alright.

826
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,320
I understand you.

827
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:27,719
Given the current situation,

828
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:28,960
there's nothing you can do.

829
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:31,360
As long as the anti-Japanese elements aren't eliminated,

830
00:40:32,039 --> 00:40:34,159
we'll keep suspecting each other.

831
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:36,039
Before the Japanese even make a move,

832
00:40:36,159 --> 00:40:37,239
these miserable lives of ours

833
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:39,719
will end up being ruined by our own people sooner or later.

834
00:40:40,719 --> 00:40:41,920
To be honest,

835
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:43,719
there's no problem with your wife.

836
00:40:44,719 --> 00:40:46,079
I'm even happier than you are.

837
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:47,679
How about this:

838
00:40:47,719 --> 00:40:49,079
After the peace conference is over,

839
00:40:49,119 --> 00:40:50,719
I'll personally ask the director for your leave.

840
00:40:51,639 --> 00:40:53,159
You're about to get married soon.

841
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:54,880
You can't always be on the front lines.

842
00:40:57,599 --> 00:40:59,079
Now that's something reasonable.

843
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,079
That's true.

844
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,320
The brothers

845
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:03,000
are already so tense they're about to lose it.

846
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:04,719
We really do need a couple of days off.

847
00:41:04,719 --> 00:41:05,679
I'll do as you say.

848
00:41:05,679 --> 00:41:06,320
Let's go.

849
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:38,800
How is it?

850
